message.content:
We only have one clear statement about Diana and one about Linda. The information given is:

• “Frank is Diana’s ancestor.”
• “Kelly is Linda’s descendant.”

There is no information that links Diana’s family line (i.e. the chain of ancestors or descendants of Diana) with Linda’s family line (the chain of ancestors or descendants of Linda). Although many relationships are given among many individuals, none of them provide a connection between Diana and Linda. There is no chain of “ancestor‐or‐descendant” relationships that shows one is an ancestor/descendant of the other or that they share a common descendant or a common ancestor.

Thus, none of the choices 1–4 is supported by the given information.

<ANSWER>5</ANSWER>
